ia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Malone, Richard and Hong posted 43.399 points total on parallel bars, the team's third rotation.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Malone scored 14.166 in his signature event, the high bar, including a beautiful dismount with two twists, two flips laid out and stuck landing.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA fell just short of Japan in the floor exercise.\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1128, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.813434407659395, \"rank\": 0.22935404702556228, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1156, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.6851984424394774, \"rank\": 0.4577350102756675, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Juda, Hong and Richard's performances earned 42.799 combined points.\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the final rotation, Team USA seemingly saved the best for last with the 25-year-old pommel horse \\\"specialist\\\" Nedoroscik, who scored 14.866 with a stuck landing in his only rotation for the team event during the 2024 Paris Games.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.813434407659395, \"rank\": 0.22935404702556228, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His impressive finish combined with Brody and Juda's routines in that rotation earned 42.466 total, which put Team USA in the bronze medal spot.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brody_Jenner\", \"score\": 0.7874730034238581, \"rank\": 0.26341170759970006, \"text\": \"Brody\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brody_Jenner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brody_Jenner\"}, {\"begin\": 1599, \"end\": 1607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.813434407659395, \"rank\": 0.22935404702556228, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brody Malone  The 24-year-old Stanford University graduate made his Olympics debut at the pandemic-delayed Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1635, \"end\": 1640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brody_Jenner\", \"score\": 0.7874730034238581, \"rank\": 0.26341170759970006, \"text\": \"Brody\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brody_Jenner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brody_Jenner\"}, {\"begin\": 1641, \"end\": 1647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"score\": 0.9984080507221788, \"rank\": 0.001335270258133398, \"text\": \"Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}, {\"begin\": 1665, \"end\": 1684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"score\": 0.9999999669132654, \"rank\": 3.3082305081406344e-08, \"text\